cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on MANETs, which is a type of wireless network, and proposes a new approach to improve the security of the DSR routing protocol. 
2. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper deals with the security issues in wireless networks and proposes a solution to detect and isolate misbehavior attacks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed approach employs Artificial Immune System (AIS) to defend against black hole attacks. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new algorithm to improve the security of the DSR routing protocol. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The proposed approach involves identifying and isolating malicious nodes in a MANET, which can be seen as a control problem.
